title: Saucon Valley's Ryan Meyers is fans' choice for Week 5 MVP
text:
Ryan Meyers (lehighvalleylive.com file photo) By lehighvalleylive sports staff View/Post Comments 
Playing on the offensive line is typically a position that doesn’t yield a ton of glory. This week, however, the lehighvalleylive football fans rewarded a standout lineman. 
Saucon Valley junior guard Ryan Meyers was voted Week 5’s standout performer on the gridiron for his play in a victory over Northwestern Lehigh. 
Meyers anchored a line that cleared the way for 418 rushing yards (279 by tailback Evan Culver).
